trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> or an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref> within an XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Representa um elemento de extensibilidade adicionado a um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"> </xref> ou um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"> </xref> dentro de um serviço Web XML.

trans-unit.source: It specifies the SOAP header types used to transmit error information within the SOAP header.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o cabeçalho SOAP tipos usados para transmitir informações de erro no cabeçalho SOAP.

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre como especificar protocolos para XML Web services, consulte [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre WSDL Web Services Description Language (), consulte a especificação em http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a URI representing the encoding style used to encode the error message for the SOAP header.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um URI que representa o estilo de codificação usado para codificar a mensagem de erro para o cabeçalho SOAP.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property should be set only if the value of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding.Use%2A> property is `Encoded`.
trans-unit.target: O valor dessa propriedade deve ser definido somente se o valor de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding.Use%2A>é de propriedade `Encoded`.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding.Use%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise the XML Web service will exhibit unexpected behavior.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, o XML Web Services exibirá um comportamento inesperado.

trans-unit.source: A string containing a URI.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres contendo um URI.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: O valor padrão é uma cadeia de caracteres vazia ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value specifying the name of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Message"></xref> within the XML Web service to which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding"></xref> applies.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que especifica o nome do <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Message"> </xref> dentro do serviço da Web em XML para o qual o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding"> </xref> se aplica.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName> representing the name of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Message"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>que representa o nome do <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Message"> </xref>.</xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref:System.String.Empty>.
trans-unit.target: O valor padrão é <xref:System.String.Empty>.</xref:System.String.Empty>

trans-unit.source: Get or sets a URI representing the location of the specifications for encoding content not specifically defined by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding.Encoding*> property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um URI que representa o local das especificações de codificação de conteúdo não especificamente definido pelo <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding.Encoding*>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding.Encoding*>

trans-unit.source: This property will return an empty string ("") if the property value has not been set.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade retornará uma cadeia de caracteres vazia ("") se o valor da propriedade não foi definido.

trans-unit.source: The value should only be set if the value of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderBinding.Use%2A> property is `Encoded`.
trans-unit.target: O valor deve ser definido somente se o valor de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderBinding.Use%2A>é de propriedade `Encoded`.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderBinding.Use%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise the XML Web service will exhibit unexpected behavior.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, o XML Web Services exibirá um comportamento inesperado.

trans-unit.source: Returns a string representing a URI.
trans-unit.target: Retorna uma cadeia de caracteres que representa um URI.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating which <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> within the XML Web service the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding"></xref> applies to.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que indica qual <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"> </xref> em XML Web Services o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding"> </xref> se aplica.

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> to which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding"></xref> applies.
trans-unit.target: O nome do <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"> </xref> ao qual o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderFaultBinding"> </xref> se aplica.

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether the header is encoded using rules specified by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderBinding.Encoding*> property, or is encapsulated within a concrete schema.
trans-unit.target: Especifica se o cabeçalho é codificado usando as regras especificadas o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderBinding.Encoding*>propriedade, ou é encapsulado em um esquema concreto.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapHeaderBinding.Encoding*>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Uma da <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse"> </xref> valores.
